=Episode 7=

00:01:11.519 --> 00:01:12.760
The new Emperor Shi Yu ordered

00:01:12.920 --> 00:01:15.000
to exterminate all of us from Pingxiang.

00:01:15.920 --> 00:01:16.960
Our presence here

00:01:17.319 --> 00:01:18.624
may not be safe.

00:01:18.719 --> 00:01:19.936
We shouldn't linger here.

00:01:25.159 --> 00:01:27.439
Shi Yu grew up in Pingxiang.

00:01:27.959 --> 00:01:29.920
I never imagine he would become

00:01:30.799 --> 00:01:33.000
another brutal tyrant
just like his brother Shi Nan.

00:01:33.920 --> 00:01:35.424
I can't let anyone recognize me.

00:01:44.400 --> 00:01:45.536
What happened? Are you okay?

00:01:47.424 --> 00:01:48.352
Are you alright?

00:01:55.640 --> 00:01:56.200
You're awake.

00:01:59.680 --> 00:02:00.239
Slowly.

00:02:00.560 --> 00:02:02.519
Your face was completely ruined
by boiling water.

00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:04.319
It can't be fully restored.

00:02:05.079 --> 00:02:07.296
I can only craft you a new face.

00:02:10.280 --> 00:02:12.480
Are you also from Pingxiang?

00:02:12.759 --> 00:02:13.472
I...

00:02:15.080 --> 00:02:16.128
The new emperor's reign

00:02:16.240 --> 00:02:17.199
is marked by cruelty.

00:02:18.199 --> 00:02:19.744
He massacred fellow Pingxiang natives.

00:02:19.919 --> 00:02:20.560
Now

00:02:22.112 --> 00:02:24.120
we are the only ones left.

00:02:30.960 --> 00:02:32.352
I grew up traveling abroad.

00:02:33.520 --> 00:02:35.520
Upon returning home,
I witnessed the slaughter.

00:02:36.520 --> 00:02:38.520
My parents and relatives
all died tragically.

00:02:39.800 --> 00:02:42.400
All thanks to that tyrant Shi Yu.

00:02:47.319 --> 00:02:48.672
Do you want revenge?

00:02:49.319 --> 00:02:50.199
Kill Shi Yu!

00:02:50.272 --> 00:02:51.639
Avenge my father!

00:02:52.439 --> 00:02:55.840
- Kill Shi Yu!
- Kill Shi Yu!

00:02:55.840 --> 00:02:58.624
- Kill Shi Yu!
- Kill Shi Yu!

00:03:05.520 --> 00:03:06.439
What's your name?

00:03:07.840 --> 00:03:09.056
Cheng Ge.

00:03:38.520 --> 00:03:39.039
Good.

00:03:51.599 --> 00:03:52.160
Tell me,

00:03:53.039 --> 00:03:54.176
if they learn the truth,

00:03:54.176 --> 00:03:55.439
will they still obey me?

00:03:55.439 --> 00:03:56.599
Don't worry, Master.

00:03:57.000 --> 00:03:57.840
In the Weaving House,

00:03:57.840 --> 00:03:59.319
only I know your true identity.

00:03:59.479 --> 00:04:00.352
It doesn't matter.

00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:01.800
After tomorrow,

00:04:02.120 --> 00:04:03.800
there will be no
descendants of Pingxiang.

00:04:04.800 --> 00:04:06.560
Before they uncover the truth,

00:04:07.039 --> 00:04:08.599
let them die for me first.

00:04:10.496 --> 00:04:12.039
Well, Shi Yu.

00:04:12.639 --> 00:04:14.159
Let me

00:04:14.840 --> 00:04:16.600
send you to your grave.

00:04:26.880 --> 00:04:30.112
(Seal of the Wardrobe Bureau)

00:04:38.144 --> 00:04:40.381
(Seal of the Wardrobe Bureau)

00:04:45.120 --> 00:04:45.959
Sir, thank you.

00:04:53.720 --> 00:04:54.879
Sir, you can't go this way.

00:04:58.160 --> 00:04:59.600
Why did you leave the palace?

00:05:00.079 --> 00:05:01.360
If someone discovers you,

00:05:01.720 --> 00:05:03.279
do you know the consequences?

00:05:04.319 --> 00:05:04.960
Master,

00:05:05.319 --> 00:05:06.432
I want to know

00:05:06.839 --> 00:05:08.704
where our weaving house cipher

00:05:09.160 --> 00:05:10.144
came from.

00:05:12.560 --> 00:05:13.376
What is it?

00:05:13.959 --> 00:05:15.279
Someone discovered the cipher?

00:05:15.800 --> 00:05:16.384
No.

00:05:17.439 --> 00:05:19.040
But recently, I observed

00:05:19.199 --> 00:05:20.560
things happened in the palace

00:05:21.160 --> 00:05:22.816
and found Pingxiang rebellion was caused

00:05:23.240 --> 00:05:24.160
by someone else.

00:05:24.416 --> 00:05:26.304
You heard those edicts issued

00:05:26.304 --> 00:05:27.079
by the tyrant,

00:05:27.240 --> 00:05:27.936
didn't you?

00:05:28.439 --> 00:05:29.600
But I think

00:05:29.959 --> 00:05:30.976
the Prince Regent acts

00:05:31.319 --> 00:05:32.480
more like the true Emperor.

00:05:32.839 --> 00:05:33.440
Enough!

00:05:49.519 --> 00:05:50.120
Master,

00:05:50.839 --> 00:05:51.519
this is...

00:05:51.720 --> 00:05:53.199
You've been in the palace for days.

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:55.959
Yet now, you haven't made your move,

00:05:56.560 --> 00:05:58.680
and even defend that tyrant?

00:06:00.560 --> 00:06:02.600
When the dark line
reaches the Quchi acupoint,

00:06:03.160 --> 00:06:04.240
without the antidote,

00:06:04.439 --> 00:06:05.480
no one can save you.

00:06:06.000 --> 00:06:06.688
Go back now.

00:06:07.800 --> 00:06:09.792
Don't forget
the blood debt of Pingxiang.

00:06:09.920 --> 00:06:10.720
Without avenging it,

00:06:10.920 --> 00:06:12.199
how will you ever face

00:06:12.319 --> 00:06:13.408
your parents one day?

00:06:48.864 --> 00:06:51.904
(Imperial Weaving House)

00:06:55.439 --> 00:06:55.879
Master,

00:06:56.680 --> 00:06:57.600
everyone's in position.

00:06:58.439 --> 00:06:59.959
Are you certain about acting tonight?

00:07:00.360 --> 00:07:01.480
We worked so hard

00:07:01.680 --> 00:07:02.920
to send Cheng Ge to the palace.

00:07:03.160 --> 00:07:05.152
A rash attack might alert our enemies.

00:07:05.680 --> 00:07:07.008
It'll be much harder for us

00:07:07.120 --> 00:07:08.040
to kill Shi Yu later.

00:07:09.959 --> 00:07:12.360
Though Cheng Ge took the Quchi Poison,

00:07:13.199 --> 00:07:14.800
I know her too well.

00:07:15.560 --> 00:07:16.704
She's

00:07:17.120 --> 00:07:18.800
not fully committed to this plan.

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:21.120
We must take the risk.

00:07:22.639 --> 00:07:24.279
As long as Shi Yu lives,

00:07:25.040 --> 00:07:26.199
my torment

00:07:26.759 --> 00:07:27.879
will never end.

00:07:38.879 --> 00:07:41.408
These are the new casual garments
made by the Wardrobe Bureau.

00:07:47.519 --> 00:07:48.199
Where were you?

00:07:52.399 --> 00:07:53.160
Forget it then.

00:07:54.560 --> 00:07:55.560
But in this palace,

00:07:56.079 --> 00:07:57.199
Gao Ji's men are everywhere.

00:07:57.959 --> 00:07:59.328
Don't reveal your whereabouts.

00:08:04.240 --> 00:08:04.896
Now,

00:08:06.000 --> 00:08:06.600
you've known

00:08:06.600 --> 00:08:08.480
Gao Ji caused the Pingxiang rebellion.

00:08:09.680 --> 00:08:11.040
Our objectives align.

00:08:13.920 --> 00:08:15.872
You needn't face this battle alone.

00:08:16.920 --> 00:08:19.240
When the dark line
reaches the Quchi acupoint,

00:08:19.480 --> 00:08:20.704
without the antidote,

00:08:20.839 --> 00:08:21.920
no one can save you.

00:08:27.800 --> 00:08:28.680
What's with your hand?

00:08:29.079 --> 00:08:30.080
I'll fetch a physician.

00:08:32.600 --> 00:08:33.480
If you need anything,

00:08:34.039 --> 00:08:34.759
speak freely.

00:08:39.120 --> 00:08:40.039
Don't try to please me.

00:08:40.759 --> 00:08:41.480
I'll say it again.

00:08:42.559 --> 00:08:43.480
If I ever find out

00:08:43.480 --> 00:08:45.399
you're tied to the Pingxiang affair
in any way,

00:08:46.759 --> 00:08:48.279
I will show no mercy.

00:08:57.720 --> 00:08:58.880
(What's wrong with her?)

00:09:15.320 --> 00:09:17.519
Your Grace, your pulse
is steady and strong.

00:09:18.120 --> 00:09:19.520
Neither superficial nor deep,

00:09:19.639 --> 00:09:20.896
and smooth in rhythm.

00:09:22.080 --> 00:09:23.919
Your health is excellent.

00:09:24.440 --> 00:09:25.888
Have I conceived a royal heir?

00:09:26.120 --> 00:09:27.232
Might I ask

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:29.480
have you been taking the elixir

00:09:29.879 --> 00:09:31.904
I prescribed last time properly?

00:09:32.240 --> 00:09:33.480
I've been taking it every day.

00:09:34.440 --> 00:09:35.240
Well...

00:09:35.799 --> 00:09:36.864
It makes no sense.

00:09:37.559 --> 00:09:39.120
That's a rare medicine,

00:09:39.759 --> 00:09:41.679
guaranteed to help conception.

00:09:42.200 --> 00:09:43.520
Unless...

00:09:54.559 --> 00:09:57.480
Unless His Majesty
has not lain with you.

00:10:16.840 --> 00:10:17.519
(Cheng Ge,)

00:10:18.519 --> 00:10:20.720
(why sacrifice yourself
for a puppet Emperor)

00:10:21.480 --> 00:10:22.799
(who clings to life in disgrace?)

00:10:23.720 --> 00:10:24.320
(But)

00:10:25.000 --> 00:10:27.200
(if Shi Yu bears
no responsibility in this,)

00:10:28.360 --> 00:10:28.919
(wouldn't I)

00:10:28.919 --> 00:10:30.720
(be a villain who kills the innocent?)

00:10:36.240 --> 00:10:36.960
Take her away!

00:10:38.720 --> 00:10:39.616
What are you doing?

00:10:40.039 --> 00:10:43.159
The Empress's orders
require no explanation to you.

00:10:43.600 --> 00:10:44.000
Go.

00:10:44.200 --> 00:10:44.799
Let go of me.

00:10:46.559 --> 00:10:47.279
I'll walk myself.

